{"tid":1810910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［武漢肺炎］由武漢返港出現嚴重肺炎或發燒症狀增至八宗","createTime":"2020-01-04T09:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T10:19:48.000Z","uid":216992,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2289b44497e60b9b558501977a44d1ac754bf6","tid":1810910,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841ed6100cd69f8f85139a08e6c0a04839b6fbc4","tid":1810910,"uid":216992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ok1tnBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fok1tnBY.jpg&h=d299464f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c783e9db8e4577ca232112b7fbb6720194cdda6e","tid":1810910,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:02:42.000Z","msg":"應該唔止咁少"},{"pid":"40bb21bf1bf50620477a55537539bf1cc9f97ad2","tid":1810910,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"邊有嚴重兩個字？"},{"pid":"ffa4cb2e9e4e42c6729be1b395b592a4f83fc5ff","tid":1810910,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"40bb21bf1bf50620477a55537539bf1cc9f97ad2","tid":1810910,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"邊有嚴重兩個字？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"手機語音打字彈出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔記得刪"},{"pid":"4cd9d9c6f53c2b319d457f3f60d95855955f165c","tid":1810910,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【武漢非典型肺炎】何栢良憂春運令武漢非典型肺炎擴散 <br />\n張建宗： 暫毋須減往來武漢及香港的航班及高鐵班次</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500976-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500976-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=54c50cf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500976-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de7f8a0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500976-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，有充分理由分析，武漢非典型肺炎爆發涉及新型病毒，相信當地有發生懷疑涉及人傳人的情況，病毒亦有一定的殺傷力，認為本港要當作病毒可以人傳人的情況應對。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，春運期間有機會令武漢非典型肺炎病毒進一步擴散，情況令人擔心，亦估計，如果源頭是來自野味或野生動物，會透過供應鏈傳到其他內地省市，希望內地政府有最新資訊，會盡快全面公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=02eb9d9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f12675f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，政府已就武漢不明病毒性肺炎個案作出高度戒備，啟動嚴重應變級別，亦不斷與內地方面聯繫，強調不會掉以輕心，如出現爆發時可以即時回應。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，最重要是防疫把關工作及注意個人衞生，現階段無必要減少來往武漢及香港的航班及高鐵班次。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於教育局局長楊潤雄早前接受訪問時說，如果有校長不勝任，局方可以取消他的校長資格，張建宗說，老師的質素及品行很重要，當局已清楚表明以學生福祉及教師專業為出發點，強調絕無半點針對老師，不存在白色恐怖。"},{"pid":"00571728f7850c3acae2ad40e205dbdeed7b9093","tid":1810910,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cd9d9c6f53c2b319d457f3f60d95855955f165c","tid":1810910,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=